"{\"abstract\":\"With about 100 million people using it recently, SVCD(Smart Voice Controlled Device) are becoming demotic. Whether at home or in an office, usually, multiple appliances are under the control of a single SVCD and several people may manipulate an SVCD simultaneously. However, present SVCD fails to handle them appropriately. In this paper, we propose a novel framework for SVCD to eliminate orders\\u2019 ambiguity for single user or multi-user. We also design an algorithm combining Word2Vec and emotion detection for the device to wipe off ambiguity. Finally, we apply our framework into a virtual smart home scene and the performance of it indicates that our strategy resolves the problems commendably.\",\"arxivId\":null,\"authors\":[{\"authorId\":\"38717208\",\"name\":\"Kehua Lei\",\"url\":\"https://www.semanticscholar.org/author/38717208\"},{\"authorId\":\"145745100\",\"name\":\"Tianyi Ma\",\"url\":\"https://www.semanticscholar.org/author/145745100\"},{\"authorId\":\"49222432\",\"name\":\"Jia Jia\",\"url\":\"https://www.semanticscholar.org/author/49222432\"},{\"authorId\":\"22703278\",\"name\":\"Cunjun Zhang\",\"url\":\"https://www.semanticscholar.org/author/22703278\"},{\"authorId\":\"50109754\",\"name\":\"Zhihan Yang\",\"url\":\"https://www.semanticscholar.org/author/50109754\"}],\"citationVelocity\":0,\"citations\":[],\"corpusId\":199466088,\"doi\":\"10.24963/ijcai.2019/948\",\"fieldsOfStudy\":[\"Computer Science\"],\"influentialCitationCount\":0,\"is_open_access\":true,\"is_publisher_licensed\":false,\"paperId\":\"5c0bd113a125192cfbfe95dd36637008165e9239\",\"references\":[{\"arxivId\":null,\"authors\":[{\"authorId\":\"26151182\",\"name\":\"C. Myers\"},{\"authorId\":\"10665310\",\"name\":\"Anushay Furqan\"},{\"authorId\":\"35704894\",\"name\":\"Jessica Nebolsky\"},{\"authorId\":\"3164224\",\"name\":\"Karina Caro\"},{\"authorId\":\"35187206\",\"name\":\"J. Zhu\"}],\"doi\":\"10.1145/3173574.3173580\",\"intent\":[],\"isInfluential\":false,\"paperId\":\"9